Cell["\<\
velocity integrals, these take a minute or so. Compute once and save the \
results\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.951842264194518*^9, 3.951842277279786*^9}, {
  3.9518424227399206`*^9, 3.9518424255718985`*^9}, {3.984240259504013*^9, 
